data.description: FIRST END-UNIT resale in Urban Square at South Lawn!  Popular Willmington "B" floor plan by Walker Anderson Homes, LLC.  Owner contracted prior to drywall stage and was able to add many builder upgrades!   Walk to all of your favorite restaurants and shops on the Downtown Lawrenceville Square!  NO CARPET - Wide-plank Revwood Laminate flooring through-out + Hardwood staircases w/stylish iron railings. Two-story foyer views dining room.  Custom white painted cabinets w/elegant curved vent hood by Custom Design Kitchens. Wall oven/microwave w/separate gas cooktop.  Oversized "Luxury" Island kitchen features quartz countertops, pendant lighting, wine fridge, under cabinet lighting, pot filler and SS farmhouse sink viewing great room leading to covered porch and grilling deck. White brick fireplace w/cedar mantle flanked by built-in bookcases. Upstairs laundry. Primary Suite w/walk-in closet and spacious bath featuring quartz counters, upgraded level 2 tile, frameless shower w/double shampoo niche! Two additional secondary bedrooms and full bath on top floor.  Terrace level w/4th bedroom and 3rd full bath.  2" blinds through-out.  Floor outlet added in great room floor as well as covered porch ceiling for future TV.  END unit adds extra windows in Great Room and oversized upstairs hallway area.
